{"tid":1625120,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"緊急！五毛進化左！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:15:44.000Z","uid":104357,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4b5ee3e283e392c1ad2063ec02791a995c0b79","tid":1625120,"uid":104357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"巴絲諗下點解連登呢排可以風向咁一致？<br />\n風向一致重來唔係好事<br />\n因為班五毛係一定會出黎反對<br />\n點解五毛重來都無消失過，但風向係一致？？？<br />\n所以風向一致=成功俾人帶到風向<br />\n<br />\n今朝就係一個好例子<br />\n琴日個個都玩到咁夜<br />\n邊個得閒一早開post 話要休息<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再者無一個tg gp 有傾過話要休息</span></span><br />\n<br />\n晏就就開始多人出黎問點解要休息<br />\n開始出現唔同嘅聲音<br />\n有人建議要去貼文宣，推post 出國際戰線<br />\n有人發動和理非今日出去反對蒙面法<br />\n呢個先係正常連登 百花齊放<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 宜家連登俾人帶風向帶得好勁<br />\n五毛進化咗！ 會開行動post 分化<br />\n再認真post 入面煽風點火<br />\n想兩邊鬧架！<br />\n所以我地都要進化！<br />\n麻煩大家睇連登要配合其他資訊平台<br />\n唔好俾人帶到風向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3cbd0201e4c84809fd3f66afde2763bab2bcbf49","tid":1625120,"uid":128569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"玩到咁夜=邊有可能咁早開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoodest logic"},{"pid":"6991ae609dc79dbace81e25353a3edd3d088e2f0","tid":1625120,"uid":104357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc3ba3c174243a6a34b8ab5fcd54f152e25e42c5","tid":1625120,"uid":5258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"啲五毛真係升級左<br />\n好多人畀人帶到風向<br />\n有無發現近兩日示威smooth左<br />\n因為上唔到連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869577a466ff595aaf7f12b2ae93bf3a30fbeaee","tid":1625120,"uid":147002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"連登吹緊既風向真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8198f8586fe69831ce6a86744172fa76e06873","tid":1625120,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3965e952fcd03d6473e775295bfe9ae6a26bfe36","tid":1625120,"uid":104357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"好多人開始唔睇連登<br />\n淨睇tg <br />\n其實咁係好危險<br />\n好多老一輩淨係識睇連登<br />\n如果越黎越少人同五毛對抗<br />\n連登就只係得返五毛嘅聲音"},{"pid":"e887ce0a387b5e774df4f5f8855dc17747eecf40","tid":1625120,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}